CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Handsome Pair - Mr. and Mrs. Edward T. Prather following their marriage Nov. 12. The bride is the former Miss Constance Louise Boyd. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men, including Edward T. Prather wearing light colored bow tie and three women, including smiling Constance Louise Prather (Boyd) wearing headpiece with mid length veil, long sleeved gown with floral lace overlay and crinoline skirt, holding book with ribbons and flowers, posed in front of fireplace in interior, possibly on Dinwiddie Street, Hill District
